Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.56,CHI,,0,0,0,,坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.61,CHI,,0,0,0,,給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:19.85,CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fnDFKaiXBold-B5\pos(640,311.333)}永別了 坂本君
